OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fand the first part of the night will
OL,7,Fsee showers or some longer spells of
OL,8,Frain. Becoming drier and clearer later
OL,9,Fin the night.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FAny isolated showers at
OL,12,Ffirst dying out then all areas will
OL,13,Fhave a dry day with variable amounts
OL,14,Fof cloud and sunny spells.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDry on
OL,17,FSunday and Monday with some warm
OL,18,Fspells of sunshine. Becoming cloudier
OL,19,Fon Tuesday.
